| `ubs` | UBS | `.xlsx` | `scrapers\UBS_extractor.py` | `providers\UBS\extract_ubs_fields.py` |
| `spdr` | SPDR / State Street | `.xlsx` | `scrapers\spdr_collector.py` | `providers\SPDR\extract_spdr_fields.py` |
| `hsbc` | HSBC Asset Management | `.json` | `scrapers\hsbc_extractor.py` | `providers\hsbc\extract_hsbc_fields.py` |
| `jpmorgan` | J.P. Morgan | `.json` | `scrapers\jpmorgan_extractor.py` | `providers\jpmorgan\extract_jpmorgan_fields.py` |
| `landg` | L&G | export file | `scrapers\LandG_extractor.py` | `providers\landg\extract_LandG_fields.py` |
