| `wisdomtree` | WisdomTree | `.json` | `scrapers\wisdomtree_extractor.py` | `providers\wisdomtree\extract_wisdomtree_fields.py` |
| `vanguard` | Vanguard | `.json` | `providers\vanguard\download_vanguard.py` | `providers\vanguard\extract_vanguard_fields.py` |
